{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be futuristic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Quantum Echo Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #ff0000; /* Pure red */\n            --secondary-color: #e60000; /* Slightly darker red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark background */\n            --accent-color: #ff4d4d; /* Lighter red for highlights */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 60vh;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 70%);\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero-title {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-color), 0 0 40px var(--brand-color);\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n\n        .hero-subtitle {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            transform: scale(1.05);\n        }\n\n        .content-section {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 3;\n        }\n\n        .section-title {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-title {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-description {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .listen-button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .listen-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #101010;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: auto;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 4;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        /* Animations */\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.7; }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 1; }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.7; }\n        }\n\n        .hero-title {\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&display=swap');\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header class=\"hero-section\">\n        <h1 class=\"hero-title\">Quantum Echo Network</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-subtitle\">Where Ideas Resonate Across Dimensions</p>\n        <a href=\"#podcasts\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Shows</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n        <section id=\"podcasts\" class=\"content-section\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">Featured Podcasts</h2>\n            <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <h3 class=\"podcast-title\">Chrono-Voyage</h3>\n                    <p class=\"podcast-description\">Journey through time with captivating stories and expert analyses of historical events. Each episode is a leap into the past.</p>\n                    <button class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <h3 class=\"podcast-title\">Astro-Linguistics</h3>\n                    <p class=\"podcast-description\">Decoding the potential languages of extraterrestrial civilizations. Exploring the science and philosophy of alien communication.</p>\n                    <button class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <h3 class=\"podcast-title\">Quantum Entanglements</h3>\n                    <p class=\"podcast-description\">Discussions on the bizarre and fascinating world of quantum physics, explained for the curious mind. Unraveling the universe's deepest secrets.</p>\n                    <button class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <h3 class=\"podcast-title\">Cybernetic Dreams</h3>\n                    <p class=\"podcast-description\">Exploring the future of artificial intelligence, robotics, and consciousness. What does it mean to be human in an increasingly digital world?</p>\n                    <button class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"content-section\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,0,0,0.05); border-top: 1px solid var(--secondary-color); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">Join the Network</h2>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.1em; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n                Are you a creator pushing the boundaries of audio? The Quantum Echo Network is looking for innovative voices to join our growing family.\n            </p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;\">Submit Your Podcast</a>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2142 Quantum Echo Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Broadcasting the future, one podcast at a time.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}